{"tid":1776601,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【警世】白宮聯署個個簽，德國聯署冇人理？","createTime":"2019-12-09T15:58:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T23:06:57.000Z","uid":334606,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"92cb402d0a71a19c4ca544438fc5184ebf8b2b13","tid":1776601,"uid":334606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:58:27.000Z","msg":"代朋友post<br />\n<br />\n[屌人po慎入]<br />\n唔好意思我係想屌下人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />作為一個住係德國既香港人，早兩日睇到下面呢個po果時其實好撚嬲好失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/globalsolidarityHK/videos/2480238905582257/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FglobalsolidarityHK%2Fvideos%2F2480238905582257%2F&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F0zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=fcaf4040\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/globalsolidarityHK/videos/2480238905582257/</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點解白宮聯署就個個簽個個傳，德國聯署就冇人理?</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係，德國甚至成個歐盟係冇美國咁大影響力，好啦，咁係咪咪美國人權法過左喇，其他地方就唔理喇?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係，簽德國petition係麻煩少少，白宮既10秒搞掂，德國要reg ac要填三填四應該要用幾分鐘。咁因為要用你幾分鐘所以就唔理? 香港人，唔撚係呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解德國既煩咁多，係因為要整份online petition出黎首先就要國會批，睇左你唔係9up 9寫 (淨係咁都要唔少時間)，先會可以publish出黎比人聯署，唔係好似白宮咁呀豬呀狗都可以上去開一份吠。而國會既petition係4星期內有5萬個聯署，國會就要開聽證會，真係做野，唔係白宮咁，簽夠都可以hea覆你兩句就收檔。我唔會話簽夠開個會就一定有d咩成果，但係點解淨係噤幾個制咁都唔試下??<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知道要簽一份德文既野可能唔係咁方便，已經有人整埋教學整哂片教大家點填，又有人話其實chrome translate都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聯署程序的教學短片(中文版)︰<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZgO58nZs0vM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZgO58nZs0vM&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F0zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=54c41003\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZgO58nZs0vM</a><br />\nEnglish teaching video for signing the petition: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/c3rSaJzd_8o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fc3rSaJzd_8o&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F0zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=25788880\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/c3rSaJzd_8o</a><br />\n<br />\n我睇住柏林人同好多有心既居德港人，呢半年黎做左咁多野撐香港，去到依家要大家簽個名，但係冇人理。除左失望，真係冇撚野好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗起兩個幾月前，台灣人係德國國會一份請願德台建交既petition，人地4星期限期内3/4既時間已經簽夠左數。睇下依家香港，限期一半過左 連十份之一既數都冇。得罪d講句，香港人算9數啦 你去下台灣旅行咪算囉，講咩國際線講咩全球開花??<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，如果你睇到呢度，想問個petition其實講乜? 咁請你自己噤入個po度睇啦，已經用英文譯哂出黎。其中包括左請願德國唔好向港狗提供&quot;人群管制&quot;武器，同埋revoke賣港賊既歐盟居留權/凍結歐盟資產。咪姐係話，想要個歐盟人權法囉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最最後，如果你睇到呢度，你簽同噤個制share出去叫人簽啦!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">聯署網址 Petition website: <a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/content/petitionen/_2019/_09/_23/Petition_99604.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fcontent%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_23%2FPetition_99604.html&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F0zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=ff1291b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/content/petitionen/_2019/_09/_23/Petition_99604.html</a></span>"},{"pid":"602d9daf262ab004ad7deab787de7cf88690a45e","tid":1776601,"uid":47149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:09:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc354949c115f50ec5d77294267f5cf7d7b3d1ef","tid":1776601,"uid":293097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T19:46:10.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"b50a87adb565174d8a686a9123fad3bdb39f82c9","tid":1776601,"uid":334606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T23:06:57.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到 post <br />\n幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}